data.description: WONDERFUL TRI-LEVEL with FABULOUS LONG RANGE CITY VIEWS plus VIEWS OF RED ROCKS, LOOKOUT MOUNTAIN and MT. LIONS from Primary Bedroom!! FRESHLY UPDATED with Brand New Carpet and Vinyl Plank Flooring, New Interior Paint and New Exterior Paint  **NICE & OPEN MAIN LEVEL with Large Windows for Natural Lighting  **SPACIOUS LIVING ROOM and INVITING KITCHEN with all Appliances, Lots of Counter Space including a Peninsula with Cupboard Storage, Skylight for Added Natural Lighting (including a plant shelf with built-in watering system) and a Window over the Sink  **DINING AREA adjacent to the Kitchen has a Slider to the Back Deck and Fenced Yard with City Views  **LOWER LEVEL includes a FAMILY ROOM with a Fireplace with Wood Burning Stove Insert, Sliding Glass Door that opens to the Lower Back Patio and HALF BATH with with a Window for Natural Light  **UPPER LEVEL includes the Primary Bedroom with Walk-in Closet and Ceiling Fan, Two Additional Bedrooms with Ceiling Fans and a LARGE FULL BATH with a Jetted Tub, Separate Walk-in Shower and a Skylight for Natural Light  **OF NOTE: Attic Fan; SOLAR PANELS (2021); New Roof to be installed in December 2023, New Gutters to be installed; Fenced Back Yard Parking Space on East Side of Home  **Fenced Back Yard with Mature Landscape and City View  **CLOSE TO RED ROCKS PARK and Amphitheater, Easy Access to C470 and Hwy 285 for a Quick Commute around town or to the Mountains with Skiing, Hiking or Camping  **Buyer to verify all information!
